00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:28.119
¿Es algo urgente?

00:17:30.639 --> 00:17:32.480
Jinghong, tome asiento.

00:17:51.079 --> 00:17:51.800
Jinghong.

00:17:53.159 --> 00:17:56.200
Estás cerca de la Sra. Mu, ¿no?

00:17:58.359 --> 00:17:59.159
Sí.

